title: it didn't come out as i expected
review: I was very hyped but it was really boring. It's not like a horror movie, i laughed a little. Jokes are not funny too, I was like ''i am so bored when does the movie ends??'' Overrated and unexpected boring story. I am sorry but it deserves 4 or 5 star out of 10.

title: Game Changer
review: This movie changed the industry. Made in 1999 but has better story than lot of 2019 movies... Old is good
